WEBVTT

00:00:04.035 --> 00:00:06.162
Weak stomach, Mr. Zerga?

00:00:06.996 --> 00:00:10.833
I don't believe in weakness.
It costs too much.

00:00:11.250 --> 00:00:13.795
I don't believe in questions either.

00:00:14.003 --> 00:00:17.215
Oh, really? Well then,
let me give you a tip.

00:00:17.507 --> 00:00:21.135
I wouldn't get into Terry Benedict
for too much money.

00:00:21.427 --> 00:00:23.221
He doesn't fool around.

